Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest read

Purpose:
  Print one archive object as continuous reading text.

Usage:
  spinedigest read <archive.sdpub> <id>

Contract:
  - Mutates: no.
  - LLM: no.
  - Output: plain text only.
  - Reads: chapter source text, fragment source text, summary text, node content, sentence text, or metadata JSON text.

Use `page` for object details and local navigation. Use `read` when the task is immersive reading rather than object exploration.

Examples:
  spinedigest read book.sdpub chapter:12
  spinedigest read book.sdpub summary:12
  spinedigest read book.sdpub fragment:12:0
